tip.text: Seems like a mediocre place but the asam pedas ayam was marvellous!! I could slurp the gravy away. Spicy, sour gravy & lots of daun kesum. Sambal for nasi lemak was great too. Typical home cooked👍👍
All that plus drinks, rm19😍😍 but come earlier if you want more variety. I'm happy with vegetables and fish
